data.title: Cecil G. Holmes
data.text:
Boise, ID

QCWA # 06460

Cecil George Holmes, 1910 - 2005

Cecil George Holmes was born on month day 1910, at birth place, Idaho, to George Holmes and Fannie Louise Holmes (born Turner).

George was born on October 25 1881, in Big Cottonwood, Salt Lake, Utah, United States.

Fannie was born on July 24 1882, in Fruita, Mesa, Colorado, United States.

Cecil had 2 siblings: Clarence Raymond Holmes and one other sibling.

Cecil passed away in 2005, at age 94 at Boise, Idaho.

XYL Lucille K7MKJ became a SK in 1998, not a QCWA member.

Son Cecil R Holmes #30989 held his mother's call and now holds W7DOH.
